text: Eden Erica Espinosa (born February 2, 1978) is an American actress and singer who is best known for her performance as Elphaba for the Broadway, Los Angeles and San Francisco productions of the musical Wicked. ==Other websites== * * at the Internet Broadway Database Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Anaheim, California Category:Singers from California Category:American movie actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:American television actors
